                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "app, the description may be the name of one of the user’s favorite",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "cities, such as ",
                  "type": "text"
